            "NEVER invent violence, weapons, cartels, drugs, or crime the user did not write. Bélico names the driving ENERGY and the narrative swing, not a subject requirement — the craft is the story and the nerve; the darkness in the song is only ever the darkness the user brought. A clean come-up told with full bélico drive is exactly right.",
